and hosting login. The website or app is 100% yours with no platform dependency or licence fees."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does NNC outsource any work?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Never. Every person on your project is a permanent full-time NNC employee. No freelancers, no offshore contractors. You can walk into any of our four offices and meet your team in person."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How long does a project take?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Corporate website: 3–5 weeks. E-commerce: 5–8 weeks. Mobile app: 8–14 weeks. CRM: 10–18 weeks. All timelines are agreed upfront."}}]}0:["m_-bRo9wsLZtxDBexfRsb",[[["",{"children":["privacy",{"children":["__PAGE__",{}]}]},"$undefined","$undefined",true],["",{"children":["privacy",{"children":["__PAGE__",{},[["$L1",[["$","$L2",null,{}],["$","main",null,{"children":[["$","section",null,{"style":{"background":"linear-gradient(135deg,#040E25 0%,#0a2055 55%,#0e2d6a 100%)","padding":"64px 0"},"children":["$","div",null,{"style":{"maxWidth":860,"margin":"0 auto","padding":"0 24px","textAlign":"center"},"children":[["$","h1",null,{"style":{"fontSize":"clamp(28px,4vw,46px)","fontWeight":800,"color":"#fff","letterSpacing":"-.05em","marginBottom":12},"children":"Privacy Policy"}],["$","p",null,{"style":{"fontSize":15,"color":"rgba(255,255,255,.45)","margin":0},"children":"Last updated: March 2026  ·  Nakshatra Namaha Creations Pvt. Ltd."}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"style":{"background":"#fff","padding":"72px 0"},"children":["$","div",null,{"style":{"maxWidth":860,"margin":"0 auto","padding":"0 24px"},"children":[["$","div","0",{"style":{"marginBottom":36,"paddingBottom":36,"borderBottom":"1px solid #E2E8F0"},"children":[["$","h2",null,{"style":{"fontSize":18,"fontWeight":800,"color":"#0B1F4B","marginBottom":12,"letterSpacing":"-.02em"},"children":"1. Information We Collect"}],["$","p",null,{"style":{"fontSize":15,"color":"#475569","lineHeight":1.75,"margin":0},"children":"When you submit an enquiry via our website forms, we collect your name, phone number, email address and any project details you provide. We may also automatically collect non-personal information such as browser type, pages visited and approximate location via analytics tools. We do not collect payment card information directly — all transactions are handled by regulated payment processors."}]]}],["$","div","1",{"style":{"marginBottom":36,"paddingBottom":36,"borderBottom":"1px solid #E2E8F0"},"children":[["$","h2",null,{"style":{"fontSize":18,"fontWeight":800,"color":"#0B1F4B","marginBottom":12,"letterSpacing":"-.02em"},"children":"2. How We Use Your Information"}],["$","p",null,{"style":{"fontSize":15,"color":"#475569","lineHeight":1.75,"margin":0},"children":"Information you submit is used solely to respond to your enquiry, prepare a project proposal and communicate with you about your project. We do not use your contact details for unsolicited mass marketing. You may receive a single follow-up communication after an enquiry if you have not responded within 7 days. All further communication will be on your request."}]]}],["$","div","2",{"style":{"marginBottom":36,"paddingBottom":36,"borderBottom":"1px solid #E2E8F0"},"children":[["$","h2",null,{"style":{"fontSize":18,"fontWeight":800,"color":"#0B1F4B","marginBottom":12,"letterSpacing":"-.02em"},"children":"3. Data Sharing"}],["$","p",null,{"style":{"fontSize":15,"color":"#475569","lineHeight":1.75,"margin":0},"children":"NNC Digital does not sell, rent or trade your personal information to any third party. We may share your information with our in-house team members for the purpose of delivering the service you requested. We do not share data with external marketing agencies or data brokers."}]]}],["$","div","3",{"style":{"marginBottom":36,"paddingBottom":36,"borderBottom":"1px solid #E2E8F0"},"children":[["$","h2",null,{"style":{"fontSize":18,"fontWeight":800,"color":"#0B1F4B","marginBottom":12,"letterSpacing":"-.02em"},"children":"4. Data Storage & Security"}],["$","p",null,{"style":{"fontSize":15,"color":"#475569","lineHeight":1.75,"margin":0},"children":"Your data is stored on secure servers hosted in India. We implement industry-standard security measures including encrypted connections (HTTPS) and access controls. While no transmission over the internet is 100% secure, we take reasonable precautions to protect your information."}]]}],["$","div","4",{"style":{"marginBottom":36,"paddingBottom":36,"borderBottom":"1px solid #E2E8F0"},"children":[["$","h2",null,{"style":{"fontSize":18,"fontWeight":800,"color":"#0B1F4B","marginBottom":12,"letterSpacing":"-.02em"},"children":"5. Cookies"}],["$","p",null,{"style":{"fontSize":15,"color":"#475569","lineHeight":1.75,"margin":0},"children":"Our website uses essential cookies to enable basic site functionality and analytics cookies (Google Analytics) to understand how visitors interact with our pages. No personally identifiable information is collected through cookies. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, though some site features may not function correctly."}]]}],["$","div","5",{"style":{"marginBottom":36,"paddingBottom":36,"borderBottom":"1px solid #E2E8F0"},"children":[["$","h2",null,{"style":{"fontSize":18,"fontWeight":800,"color":"#0B1F4B","marginBottom":12,"letterSpacing":"-.02em"},"children":"6. Your Rights"}],["$","p",null,{"style":{"fontSize":15,"color":"#475569","lineHeight":1.75,"margin":0},"children":"You have the right to request access to the personal data we hold about you, request correction of inaccurate data, or request deletion of your data. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at info@nakshatranamahacreations.com. We will respond to all requests within 30 days."}]]}],["$","div","6",{"style":{"marginBottom":36,"paddingBottom":36,"borderBottom":"1px solid #E2E8F0"},"children":[["$","h2",null,{"style":{"fontSize":18,"fontWeight":800,"color":"#0B1F4B","marginBottom":12,"letterSpacing":"-.02em"},"children":"7. Third-P